==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Phasing current
<hw>Phasing current</hw>. <def>The momentary current between two
alternating-current generators when juxtaposed in parallel and not
agreeing exactly in phase or period.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Phasing transformer</ent>⟦br⟧
